OL,3,CIs it the end of the road for lollipop
OL,4,Cpeople?
OL,6,FParents have expressed concern as
OL,7,Flollipop men and women could lose
OL,8,Ftheir jobs in potential council cuts.
OL,10,FIt comes as council budgets across
OL,11,FWales have become strained due to
OL,12,Fgrowing deficits, meaning local
OL,13,Fauthorities have been forced to make
OL,14,Fdifficult decisions to make up for the
OL,15,Fshortfall.
