OL,3,CIs it the end of the road for lollipop
OL,4,Cpeople?
OL,6,FBut, concern has been raised by
OL,7,Fparents and the wider community in
OL,8,FCaerphilly as the council's budget
OL,9,Fproposal for 2025/26 revealed plans to
OL,10,Fsave money by discontinuing the role
OL,11,Fof lollipop men and women in the area.
OL,13,FBilly Lee has worked as a lollipop man
OL,14,Foutside Machen primary school for nine
OL,15,Fyears and says he has been left
OL,16,F'bewildered' by the proposed cuts.
OL,18,FSpeaking to ITV Cymru Wales, he said
OL,19,Fhe understands the need to save money,
OL,20,Fbut "it's about the children, the
OL,21,Fsafety of the children as they cross."
