OL,3,CIs it the end of the road for lollipop
OL,4,Cpeople?
OL,6,FHe said: "I've done it for nine years
OL,7,Fnow and they've become a part of my
OL,8,Ffamily. They're like family to me. I'm
OL,9,Fgutted.
OL,11,F"I've got a bond with them all. I talk
OL,12,Fto them all every morning. I get to
OL,13,Fknow them... I know every child in the
OL,14,Fschool. Like I said, they're like
OL,15,Ffamily to me."
OL,17,FWanting to show her appreciation and
OL,18,Fsupport for Billy, one school pupil
OL,19,Fbegan a petition.
