OL,3,CIs it the end of the road for lollipop
OL,4,Cpeople?
OL,6,FTen-year-old Paris had been greeted by
OL,7,FBilly at the school gates since she
OL,8,Fwas aged two and knew she had to do
OL,9,Fsomething to help.
OL,11,FHer petition has gathered over a 1,000
OL,12,Fsignatures.
OL,14,FHer mother, Becky, said: "Paris came
OL,15,Fhome from school one day and told me
OL,16,Fthat Billy was potentially going to
OL,17,Flose his job. She said 'Mum, please
OL,18,Fcan we start a petition'. So we put
OL,19,Four heads together and came up with an
OL,20,Fidea.
