OL,3,CIs it the end of the road for lollipop
OL,4,Cpeople?
OL,6,FWhen he found out about the petition,
OL,7,FBilly said he became 'emotional'.
OL,9,F"I thought the job was going to go and
OL,10,Fall of a sudden the children at the
OL,11,Fschool found out about it and it
OL,12,Fballooned," he said.
OL,14,F"The support I've had from the
OL,15,Fchildren in the school, the parents,
OL,16,Fthe community even... Everytime I go
OL,17,Fout people say 'I can't believe this
OL,18,Fis happening.' I'm a little bit
OL,19,Fhopeful but we'll just have to wait
OL,20,Fand see."
