OL,6,FA spokesperson for Caerphilly council
OL,7,Fsaid: "All proposed savings contained
OL,8,Fin the council's Budget Proposals for
OL,9,F2025/26 will be subject to a period of
OL,10,Fpublic consultation, which is due to
OL,11,Fstart on 22 January."
OL,13,FThey continued: "Residents will get
OL,14,Fthe chance to have their say before
OL,15,Fthe final budget is agreed at the end
OL,16,Fof February. No decisions have been
OL,17,Fmade at this stage and the
OL,18,Fconsultation will play a key role in
OL,19,Fshaping the future of this service."
