OL,6,FThe council previously admitted to
OL,7,Fhaving a #47 million gap in the
OL,8,Fbudget, leading them to consider
OL,9,Fcutting services such as leisure
OL,10,Fcentres and libraries.
OL,12,FOther parents have also expressed
OL,13,Fconcern about the proposed cuts, with
OL,14,Fone saying: "These roads are very
OL,15,Fdangerous, This road in particular is
OL,16,Fvery busy. We get a serious amount of
OL,17,Ftraffic and unfortunately, we get
OL,18,Fsilly drivers overtaking in the
OL,19,Fmorning and it is extremely dangerous.
